## Step 1 — Add the example override profile

From the repo root:

```bash
mkdir -p examples/overrides/profiles
```

Create:

```bash
vi examples/overrides/profiles/10-minimal-override.example.yml
```

Put this in it:

```yaml
profile_id: minimal
title: Minimal Installs Override Example
install_label: Minimal
menu_target: minimal
implemented: true
show_in_main_menu: true
uefi: true
bios: true
supported_os:
  - rhel10
  - rhel9
  - rhel8
  - rhel7
kickstart_template: ks/{{ os_id }}-minimal.ks.j2
kernel_args:
  - inst.text
  - nomodeset
```

This file is just a copy/paste example for users.

